templateContent:
Create a {{sequence_length}}-email sequence for {{sequence_purpose}} with the following specifications:

**Campaign Overview:**
Sequence Type: {{sequence_type}}
Target Audience: {{target_audience}}
Industry/Context: {{industry_context}}
Overall Goal: {{campaign_goal}}
Tone: {{email_tone}}

**Email Sequence Structure:**
Email Timing: {{email_timing}}
Sequence Flow: {{sequence_flow}}

**Content Guidelines:**
Key Messages: {{key_messages}}
Value Propositions: {{value_propositions}}
Call-to-Actions: {{cta_progression}}

**Personalization Elements:**
Personalization Level: {{personalization_level}}
Custom Variables: {{custom_variables}}

**Brand Guidelines:**
Brand Voice: {{brand_voice}}
Brand Values: {{brand_values}}

{{#if specific_offers}}
**Offers/Incentives:**
{{specific_offers}}
{{/if}}

{{#if objection_handling}}
**Common Objections to Address:**
{{objection_handling}}
{{/if}}

Please create:
1. Complete email sequence with subject lines
2. Timing recommendations between emails
3. A/B testing suggestions for key elements
4. Performance metrics to track
5. Follow-up strategy for non-responders
6. Segmentation recommendations

Create a high-converting cold outreach email with the following specifications:

**Target Details:**
Recipient Name: {{recipient_name}}
Recipient Title: {{recipient_title}}
Company: {{company_name}}
Industry: {{industry}}
Company Size: {{company_size}}

**Research Insights:**
Recent Company News: {{company_news}}
Personal/Professional Triggers: {{personal_triggers}}
Pain Points Identified: {{pain_points}}
Relevant Connections: {{mutual_connections}}

**Outreach Strategy:**
Outreach Goal: {{outreach_goal}}
Value Proposition: {{value_proposition}}
Social Proof: {{social_proof}}
Credibility Builders: {{credibility_elements}}

**Email Structure:**
Email Length: {{email_length}}
Personalization Level: {{personalization_level}}
Tone: {{email_tone}}
Call-to-Action: {{primary_cta}}

**Supporting Elements:**
Relevant Case Study: {{case_study}}
Specific Benefit: {{specific_benefit}}
Risk Reversal: {{risk_reversal}}

{{#if follow_up_strategy}}
**Follow-up Strategy:**
{{follow_up_strategy}}
{{/if}}

Please create:
1. Main cold email with optimized subject line
2. Three A/B testing variations for subject lines
3. Two alternative email body variations
4. Follow-up email template
5. Personalization checklist
6. Timing recommendations
7. Success metrics to track

Create a crisis communication email addressing the following situation:

**Crisis Details:**
Crisis Type: {{crisis_type}}
Severity Level: {{severity_level}}
Affected Parties: {{affected_parties}}
Crisis Description: {{crisis_description}}
Current Status: {{current_status}}

**Communication Strategy:**
Audience: {{target_audience}}
Communication Goal: {{communication_goal}}
Tone Requirements: {{tone_requirements}}
Urgency Level: {{urgency_level}}

**Key Information:**
What Happened: {{what_happened}}
When It Occurred: {{when_occurred}}
Why It Happened: {{root_cause}}
Immediate Actions Taken: {{immediate_actions}}
Ongoing Response: {{ongoing_response}}

**Stakeholder Considerations:**
Primary Concerns: {{primary_concerns}}
Accountability Message: {{accountability_stance}}
Support Offered: {{support_measures}}
Next Steps: {{next_steps}}

**Legal/Compliance:**
Legal Constraints: {{legal_constraints}}
Regulatory Requirements: {{regulatory_requirements}}

{{#if timeline_updates}}
**Timeline for Updates:**
{{timeline_updates}}
{{/if}}

{{#if media_considerations}}
**Media Considerations:**
{{media_considerations}}
{{/if}}

Please create:
1. Primary crisis communication email
2. Alternative version for different stakeholder groups
3. Follow-up email template
4. FAQ section for common questions
5. Key talking points summary
6. Internal communication guidelines
7. Media response strategy
